{"tid":520901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[#metoo #柴田妹]漏查證據 男子被屈強姦坐牢逾2年","createTime":"2018-01-06T02:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T07:26:41.000Z","uid":26752,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"31ebc30ab68128a93641608dafd9a7afc792c8e8","tid":520901,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"英國再爆出警員疏忽致冤獄事件。男子丹尼．凱（Danny Kay）因強姦罪成後，親屬在Facebook找出可證明丹尼．凱與舉報人是自願性交的訊息。丹尼．凱坐牢逾2年，終翻案獲釋。親屬指，找出這證據不過花30秒時間，但警方竟然沒理會。 <br />\n<br />\n事主丹尼．凱於2013年被控強姦，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呈堂的是經修改的Facebook對話內容</strong></span>（好人好姐點會...<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），而令丹尼蒙受冤獄。在坐牢3個月後，丹尼．凱托兄弟的妻子麥迪遜登入其Facebook帳戶尋找證據，不消一分鐘就找出他和舉報人的完整對話紀錄，證明雙方是自願性交，而且於所謂的強姦案發生後，對方曾向丹尼．凱送上「親吻」等示好訊息。 <br />\n<br />\n新證據交予法庭後，法官認定警方採納舉報人經修改的Facebook對話，屬於誤導。在獄中近3年後，丹尼．凱終上訴成功，無罪釋放。不過，他自言已在獄中經歷一場噩夢，更因為一直拒絕罪行，而被獄方強制接受心理治療。 <br />\n<br />\n丹尼．凱獲釋後，指摘警方和整個司法制度不公，認為警方早有機會從他的手提電腦找到有關證據。他更表示，如果司法、執法部門都是如此不堪的話，那任何人都會成為像他一樣的受害者。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180101/mobile/bknint-20180101145421144-0101_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180101%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180101145421144-0101_17011_001.html&d=OozWam4SwW%2B8H43GDGsGhwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a1a6e2ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180101/mobile/bknint-20180101145421144-0101_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMan cleared of rape due to Facebook message revealing his innocence after two years in prison<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/man-rape-cleared-not-guilty-facebook-message-danny-kay-prove-innocence-prison-two-years-derbyshire-a8139936.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fhome-news%2Fman-rape-cleared-not-guilty-facebook-message-danny-kay-prove-innocence-prison-two-years-derbyshire-a8139936.html&d=OozWam4SwW%2B8H43GDGsGhwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d54ec48e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/man-rape-cleared-not-guilty-facebook-message-danny-kay-prove-innocence-prison-two-years-derbyshire-a8139936.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">@ 柴田ミチコ </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"588ec07f075916a6621564c48a5d04be33bbe1c0","tid":520901,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"如果係美國 佢應該賠幾億"},{"pid":"19817a9b60b2e85148d8abcb9e7a1c0ee025f292","tid":520901,"uid":34562,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"你班廢物仲成日話回歸英國，d警察成日砌生豬肉，呢d咁痴撚線既女權國家真係傻鳩先會想去"},{"pid":"388d68e785891ddd95817cd097c4c177299010c4","tid":520901,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/12-29-2017/_W2ZtS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F12-29-2017%2F_W2ZtS.gif&h=f08682e5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}